sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant WhatsApp as WhatsApp App
    participant PaymentGateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Merchant as Merchant

    User->>WhatsApp: Initiates payment
    WhatsApp->>PaymentGateway: Sends payment request
    PaymentGateway->>WhatsApp: Confirms payment processing
    WhatsApp->>Merchant: Notifies payment received
    Merchant->>User: Confirms order